---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | ProActive Pixels — Jose Noriega"
  description="Why Jose Noriega started ProActive Pixels — and what it means to have an automation partner who actually cares about your business outcomes."
>
  <Nav currentPage="about" />

  <main>

    <!-- PAGE HERO -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-hero-inner">
          <div class="about-intro fade-in">
            <div class="section-label">About</div>
            <h1 class="about-headline">
              Built by an Operator.<br>
              <span class="headline-accent">For Operators.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="about-sub">
              I started ProActive Pixels because I watched too many great businesses leave money on the
              table — not from bad service or bad marketing, but from processes that hadn't caught up
              to what's possible today. I knew how to fix that.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-photo-wrap fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
            <div class="about-photo-frame">
              <img
                src="/images/hero-jose.png"
                alt="Jose Noriega, founder of ProActive Pixels"
                class="about-photo"
                width="380"
                height="420"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="about-nameplate">
              <span class="about-name">Jose Noriega</span>
              <span class="about-role">Founder, ProActive Pixels</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STORY -->
    <section class="section-story">
      <div class="container--narrow">

        <div class="story-block fade-in">
          <h2 class="story-heading">Why I Built This</h2>
          <p>
            Most AI and automation consultants come from a tech background. They're great at building
            things — but they've never run a service business. They don't know what it's like to miss
            a call while you're on a job site. They don't know the feeling of following up manually
            on 20 leads and closing two of them, wondering what happened to the other eighteen.
          </p>
          <p>
            I do. And when I started learning what was possible with modern AI tools, I realized the
            gap between "what businesses are doing" and "what's now available" was enormous —
            and most businesses had no idea.
          </p>
          <p>
            The tools that Fortune 500 companies use for lead qualification, customer communication,
            and operations automation are now accessible to a 10-person HVAC company. They're
            affordable, fast to deploy, and they just work.
          </p>
          <p>
            The problem isn't access. It's expertise. Knowing which tool is right for which problem,
            how to configure it properly, how to connect it to the rest of your stack — that's
            what takes time to learn. That's what I've spent years doing.
          </p>
          <p>
            ProActive Pixels exists to bridge that gap. We find the opportunities most business owners
            don't even know they're missing, implement the right solution fast, and stay to make sure
            it keeps working. That's the whole model. No 40-page reports that sit on a shelf.
            Just results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-block fade-in">
          <h2 class="story-heading">What "Proactive" Actually Means</h2>
          <p>
            Most service providers are reactive. Something breaks, you call, they fix it.
            That's fine for plumbers. It's not fine for the automation systems that are supposed
            to be capturing your revenue 24/7.
          </p>
          <p>
            We monitor your solutions. We get alerted when something changes — an API update,
            a workflow that stopped triggering, a call volume that dropped unexpectedly.
            We fix it before it becomes a problem. That's what proactive means to us.
          </p>
          <p>
            The name wasn't accidental.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-block fade-in">
          <h2 class="story-heading">How We Work</h2>
          <p>
            We don't take on every client. We work best with service businesses that have
            real volume — phones ringing, leads coming in, teams doing manual work that could
            be automated. If you're doing $500K+ in revenue and feeling the friction of
            manual processes, there's almost certainly a 5–10% efficiency gain sitting in
            your operations waiting to be captured.
          </p>
          <p>
            The engagement starts with an honest, no-pressure audit. We look at your operation,
            map the customer journey, and identify the specific opportunities. You get a
            personalized Leak Report — the 3–5 highest-ROI fixes, ranked and explained.
            No commitment required to receive it.
          </p>
          <p>
            If it makes sense to work together, we move fast. Most clients are live within 72 hours.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VALUES -->
    <section class="section-values">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header fade-in" style="text-align:center; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 56px;">
          <div class="section-label">How We Operate</div>
          <h2 class="section-headline">The Principles We Don't Compromise</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card fade-in">
            <div class="value-icon">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">Speed Over Perfection</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              A working solution live in 72 hours beats a perfect solution live in 6 months. We move
              fast, test in production, and iterate. Your business can't afford to wait.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
            <div class="value-icon">🎯</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">ROI First</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              Every solution we implement has a clear, measurable business outcome. If we can't
              explain how it pays for itself, we don't recommend it. We're operators — we think
              in dollars and hours, not features.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
            <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">Partnership, Not Projects</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              We don't do one-time builds. We stay. Your business evolves, your tools should evolve
              with it. We're most valuable to clients who think of us as part of the team, not a vendor.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card fade-in">
            <div class="value-icon">🔍</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">Honest Assessment</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              If there's nothing worth automating in your business, we'll tell you. The audit is
              genuinely free — we don't manufacture opportunities to justify an engagement.
              Long-term relationships require honesty upfront.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
            <div class="value-icon">🛠️</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">Right Tool for the Job</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              We're not attached to any particular platform or tool. We recommend what's right for
              your specific situation — not what's easiest to implement or what we already know.
              The tool serves your outcome.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
            <div class="value-icon">📞</div>
            <h3 class="value-title">Reachable, Always</h3>
            <p class="value-desc">
              You get a real person — not a ticket system, not a 3-day SLA. When something
              matters to your business, it matters to us. We respond same-day.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-inner fade-in">
          <div class="section-label" style="color:#fff; opacity:0.75;">Let's Talk</div>
          <h2 class="cta-headline">Start With the Free Audit</h2>
          <p class="cta-sub">
            Tell me about your business. I'll personally review your operation, identify your biggest
            automation opportunities, and send you a Leak Report within 1–2 business days.
            Zero cost. Zero commitment.
          </p>
          <a href="/assessment" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">Get Your Free Leak Report →</a>
          <p class="cta-fine">
            Or email directly: <a href="mailto:solutions@proactivepixels.com" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration:underline;">solutions@proactivepixels.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ABOUT HERO */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 72px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .about-hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-headline {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .headline-accent {
    color: var(--pp-sky);
  }

  .about-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .about-photo-frame {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    background: var(--color-bg-section);
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-nameplate {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding-top: 14px;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .about-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  /* STORY */
  .section-story {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-section);
  }

  .story-block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    padding-bottom: 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .story-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .story-heading {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .story-block p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .story-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* VALUES */
  .section-values {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .value-title {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .value-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .section-cta {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--pp-navy);
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .section-cta {
    background: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-headline {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .cta-fine {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .about-photo-wrap {
      max-width: 360px;
    }
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
